extendedInfo.description: Cherry blossom is one of the most beautiful and romantic flowers. Download Lonely Cherry Blossom Tree Live Wallpaper and enjoy watching wonderful scenery with a blooming cherry tree during the night and day. ============================================================How to install:Home -> Press Menu -> Select Wallpapers -> Select Live Wallpapers -> Select Lonely Cherry Blossom Tree LW from the listThis Lonely Cherry Blossom Tree live wallpaper consists of a beautiful pink cherry tree with moving grass and wonderful backgrounds you can choose. You can choose between a daylight background with blue sky, clouds and the Sun, or a night sky with a full Moon and clouds that can be switched on and off. The cherry blossom (sakura) is Japan's unofficial national flower. It has been celebrated for many centuries and holds a very prominent position in Japanese culture. The beauty of the cherry blossom is a potent symbol equated with the evanescence of human life and epitomizes the transformation of Japanese culture throughout the ages. Beautify your phone with this happy tree and share it with your friends and family and give it five stars.  Moving sakura wallpapers are the best choice for you, so make your phone unique and lively with Lonely Cherry Blossom Tree live wallpapers!Disclaimer:This app may show notification and icon ads. To opt out, go to http://unpush.me and/or http://opt.leadbolt.com
